description:
Paperback book-sized collection reprinting three stories originally published in the U.K. Star Wars Weekly, plus the final part of Kingdom of Ice, one of the stories originally published in the magazine Pizzazz, which had not been previously published in the U.S. due to Pizzazz's cancellation. These were the first, and, to-date, remain the only, U.S. printings for most of these stories.

Contents:

Way of the Wookiee (from Star Wars Weekly #94-96)

The Day After the Death Star (from Star Wars Weekly #97-99 - later reprinted in Dark Horse's Luke Skywalker, Last Hope for the Galaxy)

The Weapons Master! (from Star Wars Weekly #104-106)

Pursuit (final part of The Kingdom of Ice, from Star Wars Weekly #60)

Paperback book-sized collection reprinting three linked tales originally published in the U.K. Star Wars Weekly. This remains the only U.S. printing for these tales to date.

Contents

World of Fire (from Star Wars Weekly #107-109)

The Word for World is Death (from Star Wars Weekly #110-112)

The Guardian of Forever (from Star Wars Weekly #113-115)
name: World of Fire
